4 \- maildir subdirectory read failed
5 \- existing mail open(2)/mmap(2) failed
6 \- creating a MAILDIR/tmp or MAILDIR/new failed
7 \- formatting mail failed
8 \- creating/writing/delivering mail failed
.
.fi
